{
  "chapter": 118,
  "chapter_summary": "使节团在雪夜准备渡河，项少龙命秦军分两队往上下游诱敌，引走燕人三千伏兵。然而红松林内早已埋伏阳泉君派来的五千杀手，趁机发动猛攻。纪嫣然率众家将护送乌廷芳、赵倩等女眷仓皇突围，春盈中箭身亡，秋盈、夏盈、冬盈三婢亦在乱剑中惨死。蒙恬、蒙武拼死护持众人抵达丘顶，项少龙与滕翼赶到后且战且退，以飞针暗器杀出重围，滚下雪坡脱险。荆俊接应众人乘木筏渡河，赵倩却在渡河时胸口中箭，香消玉殒。众人悲痛欲绝，将赵倩安葬于对岸林中。敌人与韩兵五百人携猎犬追来，滕翼提议前往荆家村补给。项少龙率残部历经二十五天艰苦跋涉抵达荆家村，受到村民热情款待。三十八名年轻猎人自愿追随项少龙。肖月潭深夜与项少龙长谈，暗示吕不韦权势膨胀招忌，松林遇袭正因此而来，提醒项少龙将来恐难忍受吕不韦所为。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为解赵人之围，燕人实在太不择手段了。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lv_xiong",
      "speaker_name": "吕雄",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太傅！一切准备妥当，可以动程了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若我是徐夷乱，现在必然非常头痛。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "他会中计吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "很快就会知道。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有动静了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_jing_jun",
      "text": "小俊你先过河探察形势，若敌人真的走得一个不剩，明早我们立即渡河。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不好！",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快随我来！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快到大河去，荆俊在哪里！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项郎！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要恋战！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "敌人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项少龙在这里！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "走！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚下去！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快走！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "蹲下来！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "三公主！",
      "tone": "悲痛",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项太傅一定要节哀顺变，异日回京，我定要相爷作主，讨回这笔血债。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jing_jun",
      "speaker_name": "荆俊",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "东南方有敌人出现，除了阳泉君的人外，还有韩人的兵马，人数约达五百人，还带着猎犬，我们得快走。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "到哪里去？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "往羊肠山尽是平原河道，我们没有战马，定逃不过敌人的搜捕，唯一之计，是攀山到荆俊原居的荆家村，在那里不但可取得骏马、干粮，还可以招徕些身手高明的猎人，增强实力，我和荆俊熟悉路途，应可避过敌人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好！我们走，只要我项少龙一天有命在，阳泉君和他的同党休想有一天好日子过。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "二哥给我拿主意不就行了吗？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "让他们觉得是由你这大英雄挑选出来不是更好吗？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们愿意追随我项少龙吗？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那由今天开始，我们祸福与共，绝不食言。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们明天便起程到横龙岭去，不过我们的文牒、财货全丢失在红松林内，这样出使似乎有点不大妥当。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_teng_yi",
      "text": "那些东西都是次要了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "今晚的月色不错，不若到外面走走！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "芳儿怎可没人伴她，你自己去吧！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "肖兄睡不着吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我这人最爱胡思乱想，晚上尤甚，所以平时爱搂着美女来睡，免得专想些不该想的事，今晚老毛病又发作。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "肖兄在想什么哩？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我在想吕爷，自从成为右丞相后，他变了很多，使我很难把以前的他和现在的他连起上来。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "千变万变，其实还不是原先的本性，只不过在不同的环境中，为达到某一目标，压下本性里某些部分，可是一旦再无顾忌，被压下的本性便会显露出来，至乎一发不可收拾。这种情况，在忽然操掌大权的人身上至为明显，完全没法抑制，因为再没有人敢管他或挫折他。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "听少龙的语气，对吕爷似没有多大好感。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "我只是有感而发，并不是针对吕相说的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙不用瞒我，你和吕爷是完全不同的两类人，我可以完全信任你，但吕爷嘛？我和图爷虽算是他心腹，可是对着他时却要战战兢兢，惟恐惹怒他。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "而且他扩展得太快了，初到咸阳时，食客门生只有七百多人，现在人数已超过五千，怎不招秦人之忌，今趟我们松林遇袭，正是因此而来。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们可说共过生死，所以不该说的也要说出来，以少龙这种重情义的性格，将来必忍受不了很多吕爷做出来的事，你明白我的意思吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "夜了！明天还要一早赶路，不若我们回去休息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 326
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你先回去吧！我还想在这里站一会儿。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "text": "那不若让我们藉此良宵，谈至天明，我也很想多了解咸阳的形势。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yue_tan",
      "speaker_name": "肖月潭",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "肖某当然乐于奉陪！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 118,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    }
  ],
